{
  "stem": "13382.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, mother and them-- there was weekly mail.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Every Friday, mother was writing them a letter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And every Saturday, Shabbat, the postman brought us a letter.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So there was never contact broken.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were-- actually, we had one, which they said that they're going-- you know, they wrote-- they collected the letters.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I think they had-- had a chance to write one letter, which we received.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But that was the last sign which we heard of them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Might, but I don't know where it is, yes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see, I've been changing so many addresses, and we are four children.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So, you know, these things easily are misplaced, or maybe they're somewhere.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, anyhow, there was a lot of sadness in our place, and we became more and more insecure.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So as the regulations worsened all the time, so--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--sorry?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, anti-Jewish regulations.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So-- it was about--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--so my father-- first of all, the business was-- my father could not work anymore.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had to be safe.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He couldn't be employed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mother had that business.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She couldn't manage this business anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was-- had to close down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They took all the licenses, everything away by stages.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father was home all the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was still some sort of activity for us to go to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was a huge city, and it wasn't felt so much anti-Semitism there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you get lost among the people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my father went up to Budapest, and my uncle went-- the other one.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they took some shoes for selling.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They always had to deal somehow something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How far was Budapest from Fil'akovo?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was 120 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so we've been going quite a lot to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
